    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a5 {className: a5; text-indent: 48px;}\n.html-preview .a6 {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a7 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a6\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">БУЙРУҚ</span></p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a6\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Буйруқ қабул қилинган сана</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a6\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#3}Буйруқ рақами</span><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"a6\" style=\" margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">{#4}Буйруқ қабул қилинган жой</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">Ходимни дам олиш куни ишга </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; font-weight: bold;\">жалб қилиш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">Меҳнат кодексининг 212-моддасига биноан ходимни дам олиш куни ёки ишланмайдиган байрам куни ишга жалб этишни расмийлаштириш.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt; color: #000000;\">Ходимларни дам олиш куни ёки ишланмайдиган байрам куни ишга жалб этиш иш берувчининг буйруғи билан расмийлаштирилади. Ходимнинг дам олиш куни ёки ишланмайдиган байрам куни ишлашга розилиги ходим томонидан тегишли ариза бериш ёхуд ходим томонидан иш берувчининг ходим дам олиш куни ёки ишланмайдиган байрам куни ишлашга рози эканлиги тўғрисидаги буйруғига имзо қўйиш орқали олиниши мумкин.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">1. </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#6}Ходимнинг фамилияси, исми, отасининг исми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> – </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#7}Ходим ишлаётган ташкилот номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">нинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#8}Ходимнинг лавозими</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> ташкилотда </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#9}Ходимни дам олиш куни ишга жалб қилиш заруратини келтириб чиқарган ҳолат</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> бажариш зарурати туғилганлиги муносабати билан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">{#10}Ходим ишга жалб қилинадиган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\"> дам олиш кунида ишга жалб этилсин. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 13pt;\">2. Ходим дам олиш куни ишга жалб этилиши муносабати билан унга ушбу даврда бажарган иши учун кунбай таъриф ставкасининг 2 ҳиссаси миқдорида ҳақ тўлансин.</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Асос:</span> Ўзбекистон Республикаси Меҳнат кодекси 209, 212 ва 263-моддалари, жамоа шартномасининг 12-банди ва ходимнинг розилик аризаси.</p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 203.50138504155px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг лавозими</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 188.21052631579px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">_________________</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 228.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#12}Буйруқ чиқарган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>(имзо)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"tab\" style=\"width: 47.2px; display: inline-block\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"margin-bottom: 0pt;\"></p>\n</div></div>",
